<package name="mesheryctl" project="openSUSE:Factory">
  <title>CLI for the meshery cloud native management plane</title>
  <description>Meshery manages the provisioning, configuration and operation of your Kubernetes clusters, workloads, and service meshes. While supporting hundreds of different types of cloud native infrastructure integrations.                                                                                                                                                                       
                                                                                                                                                                                             
